translate English day6_rkn_1b207cf6:


    br "\n I'm in a dream. I'm once again standing on muddy ground underneath a pure red sky. {w}I'm starting to feel at home in this otherwise loathsome place."


translate English day6_rkn_337441a5:


    extend "\n There's no one here giving me constant headaches. No silent stares as I enter the department office. No oppressive future, and no miserable past."


translate English day6_rkn_ccc3531c:


    extend "\n When I'm here, there is only she... and I."


translate English day6_rkn_46892ac6:


    extend "\n She's my abominable angel, a supremely pure being containing all the beauty in the world, illuminated by a divine glow."


translate English day6_rkn_0ea62940:


    extend "\n I feel extraordinarily lucky that someone as unworthy as myself was chosen to be graced by her presence. {w}I smile in gratitude, choking back the nausea that clogs my throat."


translate English day6_rkn_f091a040:



    nvl clear
    br "\n The corners of my forced smile quiver. My forehead is wrinkled in a way that cannot be reversed. {w}And no matter how much I try to endure it, I can't stop from moaning in disgust."


translate English day6_rkn_34964b05:


    extend "\n A soft hand touches my face, drenched in cold sweat. I close my eyes, and feel a deceptively beautiful voice whisper into my ear."


translate English day6_rkn_c09f45c4:


    extend "\n When was the last time I felt so at peace? {w}I've only experienced such a feeling while dreaming."


translate English day6_rkn_0873d40b:


    extend "\n The soft touch of her fingertips tracing my cheek, the sound of our hearts beating in tandem, spreading warmth throughout both our bodies..."


translate English day6_rkn_b8adae3d:


    extend "\n I dream of her death."


translate English day6_rkn_8fc97b42:



    nvl clear
    br "\n I suddenly awake, my mind still half-asleep. My eyes snap open and she's right there, {w}making me think the angel is still with me, surrounded by her brilliant glow."


translate English day6_rkn_566d80e2:


    extend "\n The glow from that light seems almost eternal, and yet the moment it fades, I remember everything. {w}And those memories bring back my forgotten fear."


translate English day6_rkn_7f846d82:


    extend "\n I cling to the angel's thin body as tightly as I can."


translate English day6_rkn_6fd8e340:


    extend "\n Two wings suddenly spread out from her back, reaching up toward the sky, and golden light flashes repeatedly before my eyes. {w}Pain tears its way through my head, so intense that it feels like my brain is shattering into pieces."


translate English day6_rkn_d9931a03:


    extend "\n I touched something I shouldn't have. And this is the punishment I deserve for doing so, as nothing more than a mere human."


translate English day6_rkn_c0307437:



    nvl clear
    br "\n Yet I'm determined not to let her go. Instead of resisting or trying to run away, she simply places her hands on my shoulders."


translate English day6_rkn_92191644:


    extend "\n The tenderness in her touch causes me to gag, the vomit I'd just barely held back spewing out from between my lips. {w}The hot mass that had been building up in my throat comes flying out, along with a massive accumulation of warm saliva."


translate English day6_rkn_255a1e46:


    extend "\n I desperately try to cover my mouth with one hand. {w}I notice my hand isn't covered by yellowish-white bile, but instead bright-red blood."


translate English day6_rkn_554a53fd:


    extend "\n It's a color I'm very familiar with, and yet its vivacity makes it stand out."


translate English day6_rkn_45438556:



    nvl clear
    br "\n It dribbles down my chin. {w}I reach up tentatively with trembling fingers to confirm what it is, but it's clearly blood, no question."


translate English day6_rkn_53dc76a2:


    extend "\n She takes advantage of my bewilderment to easily slip from my grasp."


translate English day6_rkn_338bc407:


    extend "\n And without her support, my body, tottering for balance, immediately falls onto the muddy ground. {w}The sludge clings to my face."


translate English day6_rkn_cb2de270:


    extend "\n Which is when I see something strange."


translate English day6_rkn_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_rkn_5111e05e:


    br "\n What I see are bright red intestines wrapped in a thin blue membrane, making them appear almost purple, with beautiful veins tracing the surface, and copious amounts of blood flowing through them all."


translate English day6_rkn_33376f16:


    extend "\n It's different from everything else scattered around me. That tinge of saccharine sweetness mixed with iron so unique to fresh, raw meat wafts through the air, stinging my nostrils."


translate English day6_rkn_d31fea18:


    extend "\n Am I too late? {w}Is this my fault for letting go of her hands?"


translate English day6_rkn_6f59b28c:


    extend "\n I struggle to raise my leaden head, and her bright, white light washes over my consciousness. {w}She's still standing there."


translate English day6_rkn_b417927f:


    extend "\n She's mercilessly pure and overwhelmingly beautiful."


translate English day6_rkn_e9a59404:



    nvl clear
    br "\n I lower my gaze this time, looking down at myself. {w}My abdomen has been ripped open along clearly defined marks from a blade, rope-like intestines spilling out."


translate English day6_rkn_9b753a3b:


    extend "\n Unable to process what I'm looking at, my heart simply continues beating slowly and steadily without stopping."


translate English day6_rkn_122203d3:


    extend "\n That divine light of hers approaches once more as she watches me die."


translate English day6_rkn_a8656af5:


    extend "\n I'm ashamed that my impure existence is being imprinted onto those eyes of hers, like some mental photograph."


translate English day6_rkn_c8f61ef9:


    extend "\n I close my eyes in shame and feel one of her pure-white hands reach into my exposed stomach cavity without hesitation."


translate English day6_rkn_3e7fbcab:



    nvl clear
    br "\n A pathetic groan escapes my parted lips, followed by another gush of bright-red vomit."


translate English day6_rkn_d740d792:


    extend "\n The sensation of her hand digging through my internal organs is colder than anything I've ever felt before."


translate English day6_rkn_869af9e1:


    extend "\n The sound of my blood sticking to her fingers echoes throughout my entire body, and that eerie feeling of having my spine and ribs explored causes me to shriek endlessly."


translate English day6_rkn_a0a45b7b:


    extend "\n The sensation of a cold foreign object wriggling up through my body finally reaches my heart, nestled between my lungs."


translate English day6_rkn_3238bc96:



    nvl clear
    br "\n She stretches her five fingers out wide, each one tracing my heart almost tenderly before gripping it tightly."


translate English day6_rkn_d3a22106:


    extend "\n The screams that had filled my withered throat endlessly are suddenly cut off."


translate English day6_rkn_a6a0198d:


    extend "\n My heart which has been beating so loudly until now suddenly stops."


translate English day6_rkn_b40eeb72:


    extend "\n It's enveloped in a hot, intense pressure."


translate English day6_rkn_5cf1f7d8:



    nvl clear
    "\n My eyes snap open just as I scream. {w}In a heightened state of hyper awareness, I feel as if all the blood has been drained from my body."


translate English day6_rkn_352dbd77:


    "My breathing is so heavy and out of control that I can't even wipe the cold sweat from my face. {w}The sound of my heart pounding frantically in my chest, as if about to burst right out, only adds to my discomfort."


translate English day6_rkn_c5dde036:


    "Wiping the sweat from the back of my cold neck does nothing to alleviate the goosebumps covering my entire body."


translate English day6_rkn_8540ad89:


    "I'm suddenly overcome by dread, and I peek under the futon covers."


translate English day6_rkn_5b2e2559:


    "With trembling hands devoid of strength, I slowly pull up the hem of my pants so I can look inside. {w}What I see leaves me breathless with shock."


translate English day6_rkn_2a402284:


    et "White foam is oozing out, similar to what a bug's guts might look like after having its body crushed by a tremendous force."


